title: 1910 Shreveport Team Cabinet w/ T206 & T210 Players
author: prewarsports

posts.post_title: 1910 Shreveport Team Cabinet w/ T206 & T210 Players
posts.post_content:
Vintage cabinet photo of the 1910 Shreveport Texas League Baseball team.  Photo is a large nearly 8X10 Silver Gelatin original with a large cabinet backing (slight trim to fit in older frame but photo portion is beautiful).  Includes future major league superstar Jeff Tesreau as well as T206 player Carlos Smith (from the year of his T206 card) as well as lots of other T210 players etc.  $395

(Check out the kid on the right with a fake white moustache and the super fancy Victorian Dresses the women are wearing in the Texas Heat!)
